<body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" tts:textAlign="center">
    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:31.953" end="00:00:50.308">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:50.308" end="00:00:52.703">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Woman] I think it is impossible <br/>to overestimate</span></p>
      <p begin="00:00:52.703" end="00:00:54.992">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the importance of Vidal Sassoon.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:00:54.992" end="00:00:56.129">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Man] He's probably one of the greatest,</span></p>
      <p begin="00:00:56.129" end="00:00:59.793">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">if not the greatest hairdresser<br/>that's ever lived.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:00:59.793" end="00:01:04.844">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] With raw talent and drive <br/>and ambition and just sheer guts</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:04.844" end="00:01:07.458">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I will not give up.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:07.458" end="00:01:11.009">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He built something that rocked the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:11.009" end="00:01:14.099">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Woman] It was one man <br/>with an amazing innovative idea</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:14.099" end="00:01:15.948">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that has stood the test of time.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:15.948" end="00:01:17.624">-<span tts:fontStyle="italic"> [Host] Our next guest became famous</span></p>
      <p begin="00:01:17.624" end="00:01:20.205">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">for creating The Shape, <br/>The Five-point, The Bob,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:20.205" end="00:01:21.869">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and the many, many more.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:21.869" end="00:01:24.442">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- They were the styles which set him off</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:24.442" end="00:01:30.354">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">on the path to creating a multimillion<br/>dollar international corporation.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:30.354" end="00:01:33.191">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[Man] Well, he's an international <br/>celebrity really who revolutionized</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:33.191" end="00:01:35.666">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the way women of the world<br/>looked on the outside</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:35.666" end="00:01:38.096">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and how they view themselves <br/>on the inside.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:38.096" end="00:01:40.359">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] Vidal was completely established</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:40.359" end="00:01:44.177">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">as the leading person<br/>in hair in the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:44.177" end="00:01:48.550">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] Probably the biggest legacy <br/>in modern hairdressing</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:48.550" end="00:01:50.106">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">is the name Vidal Sassoon.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:50.106" end="00:01:53.082">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] He's like, I supposed, <br/>like a big deal in hairdressing.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:53.082" end="00:01:54.838">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Woman] I think if you went to Japan<br/>and asked them [chuckles]</span></p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.838" end="00:01:56.274">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">what hairdressers do you know?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:56.274" end="00:01:58.882"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">They would say,</span> "Vidal Sassoon." <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">They would know the name.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:01:58.882" end="00:02:01.436">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] It's like being a boxer<br/>in the time of Muhammad Ali</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.436" end="00:02:05.536">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">or being a physicist <br/>and working next to Einstein</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:05.536" end="00:02:07.355">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because he was that good.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:07.355" end="00:02:10.513">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Woman] We think of Sassoon, <br/>we also think liberation.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:10.513" end="00:02:13.603">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] He just seems to exude<br/>this magic around him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.603" end="00:02:16.165">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] If I was the Queen of England, <br/>I would knight him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:16.165" end="00:02:18.604">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] So much of Sassoon is a myth.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:18.604" end="00:02:23.143"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Man] I fought some great people <br/>in my time,but for me, he is</span> the person.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:23.143" end="00:02:24.974">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Yeah, he is the Messiah.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:24.974" end="00:02:30.085">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Vidal Sassoon] If you don't look good,<br/>we don't look good.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.085" end="00:03:11.883">&#9834; [rock music playing] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:03:24.395" end="00:03:32.277">-[Vidal Sassoon] You know I'm sitting here<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>reflecting really at 81.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:32.277" end="00:03:35.398">Who would've dreamt that<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>sixty seven years ago,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:35.398" end="00:03:42.494">at the age of fourteen, there I was <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in the East End of London.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:42.494" end="00:03:43.976">A "shampoo boy."</p>
      <p begin="00:03:43.976" end="00:03:49.355">And then sitting here, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>over sixty years later.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:49.355" end="00:03:53.205">And I'm wondering, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>"How did it all happen?"</p>
      <p begin="00:03:53.205" end="00:03:55.965">How did so much adventure happen?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:55.965" end="00:04:00.825">&#9834; [music playing] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:04:00.825" end="00:04:03.491">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> [Vidal Sassoon] Go back all those years, <br/>you think</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:03.491" end="00:04:08.236">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the excitement, the creativity,<br/>the people you've met.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:08.236" end="00:04:25.990">[people chatting]</p>
      <p begin="00:04:25.990" end="00:04:28.826">- [Michael Gordon] So we're gonna go ahead<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and start assembling the wall</p>
      <p begin="00:04:28.826" end="00:04:30.619">because Vidal is coming to see it.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:30.619" end="00:04:32.990">I've known Vidal about fifteen years</p>
      <p begin="00:04:32.990" end="00:04:34.887">and I consider him a really good friend.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34.887" end="00:04:38.498">I've always been in the position when<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I was the elder talking to other people.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:38.498" end="00:04:40.586">So, having someone <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>who you respect immensely</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.586" end="00:04:44.217">and who has such an impact <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>on people's lives as a friend.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44.217" end="00:04:46.366">It's rather wonderful.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:46.366" end="00:04:48.912">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The more I got to know him,<br/>I realized we had lot in common.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:48.912" end="00:04:52.381">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We were both hairdressers.</span>
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">That's how we started off in London.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:52.381" end="00:04:55.611">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Both transitioned into having <br/>product companies.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:55.611" end="00:04:58.135">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I realized that, actually,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:58.135" end="00:05:01.132">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">nobody had really recorded <br/>his achievements, his life.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:01.132" end="00:05:05.742">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So, I thought a book<br/>was absolutely necessary.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:05.742" end="00:05:07.919">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> I felt like it was really<br/>important to capture.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:07.919" end="00:05:11.277">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He had an impact on the world <br/>that no hairdresser has ever had.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:11.277" end="00:05:13.025">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He changed the way women looked.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:13.025" end="00:05:16.397">&#9834; [music playing] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:16.397" end="00:05:19.390">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This was the way books <br/>used to be produced to magazines.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:19.390" end="00:05:21.366">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">You put them on the floor or the wall.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:21.366" end="00:05:23.645">You did a layout.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:23.645" end="00:05:27.218">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I think he'll really be moved to see this.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:27.218" end="00:05:30.959">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There were series of three<br/>4-hour interviews.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:30.959" end="00:05:32.791">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Different places, different times.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:32.791" end="00:05:37.061">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The first place we interviewed him<br/>was in his house in Beverly Hills.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:37.061" end="00:05:49.091">[birds chirping] [water gushing]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.091" end="00:05:53.375">- So, you were born 1928, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in Shepherds Bush?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:53.375" end="00:05:56.659">- When I was, maybe, 2 1/2 to 3 ,</p>
      <p begin="00:05:56.659" end="00:05:58.509">my mother was evicted.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:58.509" end="00:06:03.185">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">You have to remember, <br/>it was 1928 I was born.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:03.185" end="00:06:08.562">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So in '30, '31, the Depression was on.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:08.562" end="00:06:11.713">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My father left us. Had a young brother.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:11.713" end="00:06:14.079">And unlike today, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>where we're multi-cultural,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:16.577" end="00:06:17.576">being Jewish, we stood out in those days.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:17.576" end="00:06:20.257">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We needed somewhere to live.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:20.257" end="00:06:25.440">So, she appealed to the Jewish authorities<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to take us into this orphanage here.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:25.440" end="00:06:30.714">And I spent from five to eleven<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in the orphanage,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:30.714" end="00:06:34.454">and sang in the synagogue choir.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:34.454" end="00:06:53.051">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:06:53.051" end="00:06:57.673">Hmmm</p>
      <p begin="00:06:57.673" end="00:07:03.287">Seventy two years ago, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>this is where I used to sit.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:03.287" end="00:07:05.360">I was a choir boy.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:05.360" end="00:07:11.164">The choir master, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>he'd rap my knuckles on occasion.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:11.164" end="00:07:13.073">[laughs]</p>
      <p begin="00:07:13.073" end="00:07:16.561">'Cause, you know, we were kids<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and we were naughty at times.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:16.561" end="00:07:20.573">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But they were charming services.<br/>they were very warm, very gentle.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:21.019" end="00:07:25.051">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Right now, at this moment,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:25.051" end="00:07:27.792">I don't know if I did then &#8211; <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I was far too young.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:27.792" end="00:07:31.011">But right now, I'm feeling all spiritual.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:31.011" end="00:07:38.381">There's a sense of peace here <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and it's a wonderful-shaped synagogue.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:38.381" end="00:07:43.287">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It hasn't changed. <br/>I can't think of anything that's changed.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:43.287" end="00:07:47.641">To give you just a few bars<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>of something that we used to sing,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:47.641" end="00:07:49.794">we used to go <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Hallelujah, Hallelujah.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:07:49.794" end="00:07:53.111">And the tune was<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>&#9834; [Hallelujah] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:53.111" end="00:07:55.252">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">&#9834; [Hallelujah] &#9834; </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:55.252" end="00:08:08.158">[singing continues]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:08.158" end="00:08:10.110">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What I miss most is my mom.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:10.110" end="00:08:17.459">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They only allowed me to see her<br/>once a month.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:17.459" end="00:08:20.478">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I ran away from the orphanage.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:20.478" end="00:08:24.875">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Went to my dad which is so much closer<br/>than the East End where my mother lived.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:24.875" end="00:08:29.631">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He got me back to the orphanage<br/>as quick as he could.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:29.631" end="00:08:33.347">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I could see that <br/>there was no caring or love.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:33.347" end="00:08:39.221">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> You could tell that as he walked away,<br/>when he passed me over to the authorities,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:39.221" end="00:08:42.136">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that he already had <br/>something else on his mind.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:42.136" end="00:08:44.804">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He didn't even look at me.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:44.804" end="00:08:52.001">And I think that moment, was when I lost <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>any love that I had for him.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:52.001" end="00:08:54.778">Never saw him again.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:55.409" end="00:08:58.549">- [Betty Sassoon] You see, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I had two beautiful sons.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:58.549" end="00:09:00.193">And I'd always had that feeling</p>
      <p begin="00:09:00.193" end="00:09:05.441">that I wanted my sons to grow up<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to be very proud of their mother.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:05.441" end="00:09:07.866">And think that helped me an awful lot.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:07.866" end="00:09:12.104">- If there's anything you'd wish for me<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in the future, what would it be?</p>
      <p begin="00:09:12.104" end="00:09:13.902">- Oh, God, and this is the truth...</p>
      <p begin="00:09:13.902" end="00:09:18.739">I wish happiness in your life<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>because you deserve it, son.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:18.739" end="00:09:21.405">If anybody deserves it,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that's you because you've been&#8230;</p>
      <p begin="00:09:21.405" end="00:09:23.445">to me...</p>
      <p begin="00:09:23.445" end="00:09:26.991">Please, It&#8217;s the truth the best son <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>a mother could ever have.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:26.991" end="00:09:34.097">And I think I am blessed by God<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to have such a son.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:34.097" end="00:09:36.150">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Vidal] Her life was a painful one.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:36.150" end="00:09:40.037">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Mine was different. I knew nothing else.<br/>The orphanage and then the war broke out.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:40.037" end="00:09:44.500">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Churchill] We can go on to the end.<br/>We can fight in France.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:44.500" end="00:09:46.544">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We can fight on the seas and oceans.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:46.544" end="00:09:48.645">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Vidal] And then suddenly, <br/>we were all picked-up.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:09:48.645" end="00:09:52.385">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">All the kids of London <br/>and sent to the country.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:52.385" end="00:09:55.387">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Where we lived with cows and sheep <br/>for the next few years.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:55.387" end="00:09:57.442">And of course very nice people <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that took us in.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:57.442" end="00:10:01.026">I came back to London at fourteen<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and the war was still on.</p>
      <p begin="00:10:01.026" end="00:10:04.957">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And we were sleeping down the shelter<br/>as everybody did.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:04.957" end="00:10:09.556">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And the Luftwaffe was rearranging<br/>the streets of London every night.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:09.556" end="00:10:11.803">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The architecture was changing <br/>at every moment.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:11.803" end="00:10:15.262">-<span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Churchill] We shall defend our island<br/>whatever the cost may be.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:10:15.262" end="00:10:17.580">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Vidal] I had a job as a glove cutter.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:10:17.580" end="00:10:19.387">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was cutting the little snippets</span>
      </p>
