      <p begin="01:22:15.394" end="01:22:16.936">-[Gordon] It's pretty impressive isn't it?</p>
      <p begin="01:22:16.936" end="01:22:19.063">- [Vidal] Yeah. Really yeah is.</p>
      <p begin="01:22:19.063" end="01:22:34.230">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="01:22:34.230" end="01:22:35.880">- [Gordon] You get to a certain point</p>
