      <p begin="01:23:06.644" end="01:23:11.159">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Vidal] They haven't beaten Italy <br/>for 88 years.</span></p>
      <p begin="01:23:11.159" end="01:23:17.707">So this is extraordinary if they do it.</p>
      <p begin="01:23:17.707" end="01:23:23.044">Yes! They got it. I'm pleased because<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>they deserve it.</p>
      <p begin="01:23:23.044" end="01:23:27.324">How fortuitous to be able <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to touch the human frame.</p>
