      <p begin="01:23:35.052" end="01:23:38.716">that molds, creates, spontaneous fashion.</p>
      <p begin="01:23:38.716" end="01:23:43.863">To be involved in the poetry of change, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that was the '60s.</p>
      <p begin="01:23:45.369" end="01:23:50.506">So, from my point of view,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>if you bring back the spirit.</p>
