      <p begin="01:24:01.673" end="01:24:06.598">-<span tts:fontStyle="italic"> [Announcer] Ladies and gentlemen,<br/>Mr. Vidal Sassoon.</span></p>
      <p begin="01:24:06.598" end="01:24:28.309">[crowd applause and cheering]</p>
      <p begin="01:24:28.309" end="01:24:31.593">- You know I'm sitting here reflecting.</p>
      <p begin="01:24:31.593" end="01:24:37.172">Really I'm wondering <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>how did it all happen?</p>
      <p begin="01:24:37.172" end="01:24:40.467">How did so much adventure happen.</p>
      <p begin="01:24:40.467" end="01:24:44.921">Going back all those years, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>you think the excitement,</p>
      <p begin="01:24:44.921" end="01:24:49.400">the creativity, the people you've met.</p>
      <p begin="01:24:49.400" end="01:24:55.140">The extraordinary sense <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>of loneliness at times.</p>
      <p begin="01:24:55.140" end="01:25:09.855">Most of my progressive thoughts <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in work and attitude I've been alone.</p>
