      <p begin="01:25:14.584" end="01:25:16.265">it was a dance hall.</p>
      <p begin="01:25:16.265" end="01:25:22.416">I was upstairs watching from the balcony,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>all the revelers enjoying themselves.</p>
      <p begin="01:25:22.416" end="01:25:26.490">I was looking down on maybe <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>a thousand or more people.</p>
      <p begin="01:25:26.490" end="01:25:28.927">I didn't feel part of the crowd.</p>
      <p begin="01:25:28.927" end="01:25:37.597">In my own loneliness, there was always<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>this sense that I wanted to be a winner.</p>
