      <p begin="01:25:43.049" end="01:25:46.798">My heart was in hair.</p>
      <p begin="01:25:46.798" end="01:25:50.233">Always has been, still is.</p>
      <p begin="01:25:50.233" end="01:25:53.884">You know tomorrow is gonna be a day<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that has never ever happened to me before.</p>
      <p begin="01:25:53.884" end="01:26:00.547">Actually going to the Palace<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to see the CB from the Queen.</p>
      <p begin="01:26:00.547" end="01:26:07.506">The more I think about it, the more I <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>sense that it truly belongs to the craft.</p>
