      <p begin="01:26:27.484" end="01:26:31.766">- I laugh and say to myself,</p>
      <p begin="01:26:31.766" end="01:26:34.763">"God, I wish I had <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the second original idea."</p>
      <p begin="01:26:34.763" end="01:26:39.537">I would love to see some young person<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>on enormous energy,</p>
